# Docker redeploy

When you finish edits that affect the running game (anything under `sockets/`, `express/`, `public/`, `gameSettings.js`, `Dockerfile`, or `docker-compose.yml`), run a redeploy before considering the task done:

```bash
npm run redeploy
```

Same as `docker compose up -d --build` from the repo root. Do not only describe redeploy steps to the user—execute them unless they explicitly ask not to.
